  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      WP2.1. PK/PD target attainment Plasma exposure ELF exposure WP2.2. Predictive dosing
      algorithm WP2.3. Validation WP2.4. ECMO subset
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      First, We will document exposure to ceftriaxone in plasma and epithelial lining fluid.

      Second, we will try to identify risk factors for not attaining PK/PD target. Based on
      significant predictors for target non attainment we will construct a predictive dosing
      algorithm.

      In a next step this dosing algorithm will be validated in another set of ICU patients.

      Finally in a small subset of ECMO patients PK exposure will be explored.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
